		{
			dependencies: ["3BAA6E1DEABA9E59"]
			description: ["The Tang Sect's hidden weapons are forged at the Forging Table using Spirit Iron and specialized components. Unlike conventional combat, hidden weapons strike from concealment — each one has unique trigger mechanics, effective ranges, and soul power cost. Mastery of the Forging Table is the first step into Tang Sect doctrine."]
