		{
			dependencies: [
				"0194FAB6E9EFFA13"
				"792CE5342E2F27E8"
			]
			description: ["The Dragon Beard Needle is a core Tang Sect hidden weapon — thin as hair, fired silently in clusters. It demands precise soul power channeling to aim; Spirit Scholar cultivation provides the baseline control required. As your rank rises, higher-tier hidden weapons become accessible, each with escalating range, trigger complexity, and raw output."]
			id: "0CB6D79172FC5B93"
