		{
			dependencies: ["9F3B5D7CA1E4F6B8"]
			description: ["Buddha's Fury Tang Lotus is the apex of Tang Sect hidden weapon design — a nine-petal lotus that seals in explosive spirit energy, detonating on impact in a pattern that covers every escape vector. It requires Level 90 cultivation to deploy and demands mastery of every preceding Tang Sect technique. The two legendary weapons — Yama's Invitation and Bodhi Blood — are single-use and drop only from the most powerful sources. This lotus is the weapon you build toward."]
			id: "A04C6E8DB2F5A7C9"
