		{
			dependencies: [
				"B15D7F9EC3A6B8DA"
				"6DACE8982D9E9FA0"
			]
			description: ["Spirit Steel is harder than any standard ore — forged through the convergence of Botania mana and Soul Land spirit_iron at the mana infusion pool. At the Forging Table, the same ingots that produce Spirit Steel Armor can produce spirit_steel weapons: the spirit_steel_sword scales favorably against beast-type enemies due to its resonance with soul power. Spirit Steel weapons also accept Mine & Slash stat souls — apply an Uncommon or Rare stat soul to unlock the stat tree for your weapon and begin allocating damage, crit, and speed points."]
